  title="Woman-Owned Canadian Web Design & Lead Generation Agency"
  description="Woman-owned and proudly Canadian. Lead Flow North empowers small businesses with modern technology to compete and win in the Canadian market. Transparent pricing, founder-led service."
  structuredData={homeSchema}
>

  <!-- Launch Pricing Banner -->
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-600 to-primary-600 text-white py-3 px-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base font-medium">
      üéÅ <strong>Launch Pricing Active:</strong> Save 50% on all website packages while we open our 2026 client roster.
