            <span class="text-base" aria-hidden="true">üçÅ</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-red-700 dark:text-red-300">Woman-Owned</span>
            <span class="text-red-300 dark:text-red-600">|</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-red-700 dark:text-red-300">Proudly Canadian</span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-tight mb-6">
            Your Website Should Be Your
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-500">Best Salesperson</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-prose leading-relaxed" data-exp-key="home-hero" data-exp-a="Stop losing customers to competitors with better websites. We give Canadian small businesses the same technology the big guys use: high-converting sites, automated lead generation, and real results. No agency markup. No BS." data-exp-b="Founder-led web design and automation for Canadian small businesses. Clear scope, fixed pricing, and a fast launch path.">
            Stop losing customers to competitors with better websites. We give Canadian small businesses the same technology the big guys use: high-converting sites, automated lead generation, and real results. <strong>No agency markup. No BS.</strong>
